# .gitignore for OpenClean (.NET 10 / WPF)
# Based on the official GitHub VisualStudio.gitignore, trimmed for a .NET desktop app.

## Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebugPublic/
[Rr]elease/
[Rr]eleases/
x64/
x86/
[Ww][Ii][Nn]32/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
bld/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

